From: Richard W.M. Jones rjones@redhat.com Mon Sep 1 18:28:29 2025 +0100
Subject: convert: Use quoted string literals in many places
Date: Mon Sep 1 18:28:29 2025 +0100:
Git: dce61d1c61fd8362a00a006a07f1f8d6a1772d7b

Use quoted string literals to make inline scripts easier to read and
write.

This change was done automatically by the script found in
https://github.com/libguestfs/libguestfs/commit/02b64d5cec1ac0a6f7627d5489996de4474a67f6

